{"tid":1283090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(代POST)我係一個社工請入嚟睇睇","createTime":"2019-07-03T17:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T17:32:37.000Z","uid":170652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"11d0a1303846f63c6399a113f3513e5b97f16a7d","tid":1283090,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:15:48.000Z","msg":"有消息指唔同網上平台都有人<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">扮社工</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請大家唔好亂同啲可疑嘅社工透露太多<br />\n我相信絕大部分同工都希望大家<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">分享自己真實嘅感受</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對大家嘅幻想或者夢境無咩興趣</span></strong><br />\n希望大家信一信好多現職前線社工真係好關心大家情緒健康嘅狀態<br />\n有咩事一定要搵人傾一傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後，天佑香港<br />\n香港人加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7721e1b07c70074628b35620ae057e52f4decfa1","tid":1283090,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:23:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ee5cda576f3aedf435afdeb907a370e32a0c5e5","tid":1283090,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:25:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2e837ef735f5118187e38a785b6e122638dd6ae","tid":1283090,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36db9660329e1db4342f4c041f964accae4fc9c6","tid":1283090,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:29:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b047e1d2eec53cb63505c8ee0332fa12a26299ea","tid":1283090,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68f11cbafd42537ab50c2ce925d9f19667806ac9","tid":1283090,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d180bfe4b7c807867f89257cebdb8713